-Preventing accidents;

-Training our employees in correct response procedures in the event of an accident;

-Participating in community emergency preparedness;

-Addressing any citizen concerns by fully explaining potential hazards associated with ETC operations and all steps being taken to prevent and mitigate accidents; and

-Being a good corporate citizen in Johnson County.

With these objectives in mind, the Risk Management Plan has been developed to provide information about our management of the risks associated with the natural gs treatment and liquids recovery process.  Most important, we stress our commitment to ensuring a safe operation for our employees, our visitors and our community.
